                            <comment id="14568405" author="ehatcher" created="Tue, 2 Jun 2015 02:26:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=esther.quansah&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;esther.quansah&quot;&gt;esther.quansah&lt;/a&gt;!   I&apos;ve tinkered with things a bit (diff my patch and your patch to see specifically) including: changed globe icon to gear simply because it was already built-in and doesn&apos;t refer to a remote resource, some minor resource properties tweaks, and additionally I added, tangentially, the extracting of e-mail addresses and URLs from file content into email_ss and url_ss fields (try &amp;amp;facet.field=email_ss&amp;amp;facet.field=url_ss).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maybe we add back a globe icon, but something small, free for us to use legally, and built-in.  Note: binary files need to be added to JIRA tickets separately from .patch files.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
